<item>
            <title>[LU-4399] quota are off but mds is checking quota</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4399</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Quota is turned off:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;rpaberna@pfe22 test&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;$ lfs quota -q /nobackupp8&lt;br/&gt;
user quotas are not enabled.&lt;br/&gt;
group quotas are not enabled.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but users are running into quota issue like this.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;rpaberna@pfe22 test&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;$ touch mahmoud&lt;br/&gt;
touch: cannot touch `mahmoud&apos;: Disk quota exceeded&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;MDS debug logs show mds is doing quota checking. See &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>MDS: 2.1.5&lt;br/&gt;
Client 2.1.5</environment>
